            "colSpan": 1,
            "rowSpan": 1
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "type": "table_cell",
            "children": [
              {
                "data": {},
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Indeterminate indicators express an unknown amount of wait time. They should be used when website performs an unquantifiable task, such as loading or synchronizing complex data or if it’s not necessary to indicate how long an activity will take.",
                    "font-style": "normal",
                    "font-variant-caps": "normal",
                    "font-weight": "normal",
                    "letter-spacing": "normal",
                    "orphans": "auto",
                    "text-align": "start",
