  {
    "data": {},
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "Behavior",
        "uui-richTextEditor-span-mark": true,
        "uui-richTextEditor-bold": true
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "data": {},
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "Spinner displays progress by animating an indicator along an invisible circular track in a clockwise direction. They can be applied directly to a surface, such as a button or card.",
        "uui-richTextEditor-span-mark": true
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "data": {},
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "text": "Integrating with actions",
        "uui-richTextEditor-span-mark": true,
        "uui-richTextEditor-bold": true
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "data": {},
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "A spinner can be integrated into a button or actionable icon to express a connection between an interaction and a specific item. They are typically used to express when an interaction, such as clicking a button again, isn’t available.",
        "uui-richTextEditor-span-mark": true
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "data": {},
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "They should be used for short, indeterminate activities",
        "uui-richTextEditor-span-mark": true
      },
      {
        "text": " ",
        "uui-richTextEditor-span-mark": true
      },
      {
        "text": "(between",
        "uui-richTextEditor-span-mark": true
      },
      {
        "text": " ",
        "uui-richTextEditor-span-mark": true
      },
      {
        "text": "2-5 seconds). Longer activities may require alternate methods of communication, such as snackbars or notifications.",
        "uui-richTextEditor-span-mark": true
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "data": {},
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "In cases, when spinner was used to submit something or sent, for example after sending contact form, after spinner has worked, sending was completed and spinner disappeared, it’s good to show some notification that the process was successful.",
        "uui-richTextEditor-span-mark": true
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "data": {},
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "",
        "uui-richTextEditor-span-mark": true
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "data": {},
    "type": "uui-richTextEditor-header-3",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "Waver",
        "uui-richTextEditor-span-mark": true
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "data": {
      "src": "http://static.cdn.epam.com/uploads/690afa39a93c88c4dd13758fe1d869d5/EPM-UUI/Images/LOD3.png",
