    "url": "http://static.cdn.epam.com/uploads/690afa39a93c88c4dd13758fe1d869d5/EPM-UUI/Images/LOD3.png",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": ""
      }
    ],
    "width": 800
  },
  {
    "data": {},
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "Behavior",
        "uui-richTextEditor-span-mark": true,
        "uui-richTextEditor-bold": true
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "data": {},
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "Waver displays progress by animating an indicator that the points gradually rise and fall. They are not as used as spinners, but can be used",
        "uui-richTextEditor-span-mark": true
      },
      {
        "text": " ",
        "uui-richTextEditor-span-mark": true
      },
      {
        "text": "for specific cases",
        "uui-richTextEditor-span-mark": true
      },
      {
        "text": ", when the spinner doesn’t work well, for example while a person is typing in chat. ",
        "uui-richTextEditor-span-mark": true
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "data": {},
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "Integrating with actions",
        "uui-richTextEditor-span-mark": true,
        "uui-richTextEditor-bold": true
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "data": {},
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "They should be used for short, indeterminate activities",
        "uui-richTextEditor-span-mark": true
      },
      {
        "text": " ",
        "uui-richTextEditor-span-mark": true
      },
      {
        "text": "(between",
        "uui-richTextEditor-span-mark": true
      },
      {
        "text": " ",
        "uui-richTextEditor-span-mark": true
      },
      {
        "text": "2-5 seconds). Longer activities may require alternate methods of communication, such as snackbars or notifications.",
        "uui-richTextEditor-span-mark": true
      },
      {
        "text": "If for some element in some place, for example a card, if you  have already used a spinner, we can’t use waver in other places.",
        "uui-richTextEditor-span-mark": true
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "data": {},
    "type": "uui-richTextEditor-header-3",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "Progress bar",
        "uui-richTextEditor-span-mark": true
      }
    ]
  },
